Disclosed are a multilevel cloud processing method and a multilevel cloud processing system for video-on-demand data. The multilevel cloud processing method comprises: A. receiving a demand for processing video-on-demand data; B. acquiring a data storage location of a processing result of all cycles with a lower level within the cycle range of the processing demand; C. constructing a classified cloud processing parameter recognizable to a cloud computing system; and D. processing the data storage location and the classified cloud processing parameter based on the type of the processing demand and storing a processing result in a history processing result database. By means of a multilevel cloud processing method in the present invention, the periodicity of the video-on-demand data is reused and the purposes of reusing an existing processing result, accelerating the processing speed and reducing the processing time are achieved.
